sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_appl_generic</ci_type><cpattern_type>2</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id/><name>Apache Enrich Attributes</name><ndl>library {
	name = "Apache Enrich Attributes"
	id = "118e7a04e4d4441ba0e64e4d0e3338d7"
	description = ""
	step {
		name = "set fs windows"
		if {
			condition = eq {
				get_attr {"computer_system.osFamily"}
				"WINDOWS"
			}
			on_true = set_attr {
				"fs"
				"\\"
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "set fs unix"
		if {
			condition = neq {
				get_attr {"computer_system.osFamily"}
				"WINDOWS"
			}
			on_true = set_attr {
				"fs"
				"/"
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "load config file to string table"
		if {
			condition = is_not_empty {get_attr {"config_file"}}
			on_true = parse_text_file_to_var {
				file_path = get_files_by_filter {
					expression = get_attr {"config_file"}
					foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
				}
				var_names = table {
					name = "config_file_1"
					col_names = "string"
				}
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					exclude_lines_pattern = "^#","    ^$","    ServerRoot","    ^<","    Listen","    PidFile","    DocumentRoot","    Options","    Allow","    allow","    UserDir","    DirectoryIndex","    Deny","    TypesConfig","    LogFormat","    ErrorLog","    MIMEMagic","    CustomLog","    Alias","    Icon","    Readme","    Header","    IndexIgnore","    AddEncoding","    AddType","    BrowserMatch","    WebSpherePluginConfig"
					selected_positions = 1
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
			on_false = nop {}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "set admin.conf file"
		set_attr {
			"admin_conf"
			concat {
				get_attr {"install_directory"}
				get_attr {"fs"}
				"conf"
				get_attr {"fs"}
				"admin.conf"
			}
		}
	}
	step {
		name = "load admin config file to string table"

sys_update_xml.name: sa_pattern_28d607dbfead4be3887c843814455100
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update sys_domain="global" table="sa_pattern"><sa_pattern action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><ci_type>cmdb_ci_apache_web_server</ci_type><cpattern_type>1</cpattern_type><description/><directory>false</directory><enforce_proc_classy>false</enforce_proc_classy><invoke_per_account>false</invoke_per_account><metadata_id>28d607dbfead4be3887c843814455100</metadata_id><name>Apache On Unix Pattern</name><ndl>pattern {
	metadata {
		id = "28d607dbfead4be3887c843814455100"
		name = "Apache On Unix Pattern"
		description = ""
		citype = "cmdb_ci_apache_web_server"
		apply_to_os_families = "cmdb_ci_unix_server","cmdb_ci_solaris_server","cmdb_ci_hpux_server","cmdb_ci_linux_server","cmdb_ci_aix_server"
	}
	identification {
		name = "Identification for HTTP(S) entry point type(s)"
		entry_point {type = "cmdb_ci_endpoint_http,cmdb_ci_endpoint_tcp"}
		find_process_strategy {strategy = LISTENING_PORT}
		step {
			name = "Check process name to match Apache"
			match {
				any {
					contains {
						get_attr {"process.executable"}
						"httpd"
					}
					contains {
						get_attr {"process.executable"}
						"apache"
					}
				}
				terminate_op = terminate
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Get home dir"
			parse_var_to_var {
				from_var_name = "process.commandLine"
				to_var_names = "install_directory"
				parsing_strategy = cmdline_linux_parsing {after_option = "-d"}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Get config file"
			parse_var_to_var {
				from_var_name = "process.commandLine"
				to_var_names = "config_file"
				parsing_strategy = cmdline_linux_parsing {after_option = "-f"}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Condition - check that conf_file was set if not extract it from httpd -V"
			if {
				condition = is_empty {get_attr {"config_file"}}
				on_true = runcmd_to_var {
					cmd = concat {
						". /etc/apache2/envvars; "
						get_attr {"process.executablePath"}
						" -V "
					}
					var_names = "config_file"
					parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
						include_lines_pattern = "SERVER_CONFIG_FILE"
						delimiters = "=","\""
						selected_positions = 2
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "If install dir empty extract it from httpd -V"
			if {
				condition = is_empty {get_attr {"install_directory"}}
				on_true = runcmd_to_var {
					cmd = concat {
						get_attr {"process.executablePath"}
						" -V "
					}
					var_names = "install_directory"
					parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
						include_lines_pattern = "HTTPD_ROOT"
						delimiters = "=","\""
						selected_positions = 2
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "If install dir empty extract from config_file path"
			if {
				condition = is_empty {get_attr {"install_directory"}}
				on_true = parse_var_to_var {
					from_var_name = "config_file"
					to_var_names = "install_directory"
					parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
						delimiters = "/conf"
						selected_positions = 1
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "default location of conf file"
			if {
				condition = is_empty {get_attr {"config_file"}}
				on_true = set_attr {
					"config_file"
					concat {
						get_attr {"install_directory"}
						"/conf/httpd.conf"
					}
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "check if the SERVER_CONFIG_FILE is relative or not"
			if {
				condition = starts_with {
					"/"
					get_attr {"config_file"}
				}
				on_true = nop {}
				on_false = set_attr {
					"config_file"
					concat {
						get_attr {"install_directory"}
						"/"
						get_attr {"config_file"}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Get Version from httpd -V"
			runcmd_to_var {
				cmd = concat {
					get_attr {"process.executablePath"}
					" -V "
				}
				var_names = "version"
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					include_lines_pattern = "version"
					delimiters = " version: "
					selected_positions = 2
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "sets the display label"
			set_attr {
				"name"
				concat {
					"Apache server@"
					get_attr {"computer_system.primaryHostname"}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "sets the display label with hostname"
			if {
				condition = contains {
					get_attr {"name"}
					"@"
				}
				on_true = set_attr {
					"name"
					concat {
						"Apache server@"
						get_attr {"computer_system.primaryHostname"}
					}
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "get version from version.signature (IBM HTTPSERVER) "
			if {
				condition = is_empty {get_attr {"version"}}
				on_true = parse_text_file_to_var {
					file_path = get_files_by_filter {
						expression = concat {
							get_attr {"install_directory"}
							"/version.signature"
						}
						foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
					}
					var_names = "version"
					parsing_strategy = position_from_end {
						tokens_from_end = 1
						delimiter = " "
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Condition - check that version was set if not extract it from httpd -v"
			if {
				condition = any {
					is_empty {get_attr {"version"}}
					contains {
						get_attr {"version"}
						"directory"
					}
				}
				on_true = runcmd_to_var {
					cmd = concat {
						get_attr {"process.executablePath"}
						" -V | grep 'Server version' | cut -d '/' -f 2 | cut -d ' ' -f 1"
					}
					var_names = "version"
					parsing_strategy = position_from_end {
						tokens_from_end = 1
						delimiter = " "
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "set version if still empty"
			if {
				condition = any {
					contains {
						get_attr {"version"}
						"directory"
					}
					is_empty {get_attr {"version"}}
				}
				on_true = parse_text_file_to_var {
					file_path = get_files_by_filter {
						expression = concat {
							get_attr {"install_directory"}
							"/properties/version/IHS.product"
						}
						foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
					}
					var_names = "version"
					parsing_strategy = xml_parsing_strategy {
						rootXpath = "/product"
						fields {
							field {
								col_name = "version"
								xpath = "/product/version/text()"
								delimiters = ""
								position = 1
							}
							field {
								col_name = "forEach"
								for_each = "forEach"
								delimiters = ""
								position = 1
							}
						}
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Remove .bin from httpd executable"
			parse_var_to_var {
				from_var_name = "process.executablePath"
				to_var_names = "httpd_command"
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					delimiters = ".bin"
					selected_positions = 1
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "ser version if still empty 2"
			if {
				condition = any {
					contains {
						get_attr {"version"}
						"directory"
					}
					is_empty {get_attr {"version"}}
				}
				on_true = runcmd_to_var {
					cmd = concat {
						get_attr {"httpd_command"}
						" -v | grep 'Server version' | cut -d '/' -f 2 | cut -d ' ' -f 1"
					}
					var_names = "version"
					parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
						selected_positions = 1
					}
					if_not_found_do = nop {}
					cache_flag = 0
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "slim version"
			parse_var_to_var {
				from_var_name = "version"
				to_var_names = "version"
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					delimiters = "/"
					selected_positions = 2
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "change slim version for suse linux"
			if {
				condition = all {
					not_ends_with {
						")"
						get_attr {"version"}
					}
					contains {
						get_attr {"version"}
						"("
					}
				}
				on_true = set_attr {
					"version"
					concat {
						get_attr {"version"}
						")"
					}
				}
				on_false = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "get short_description"
			runcmd_to_var {
				cmd = concat {
					". /etc/apache2/envvars; "
					get_attr {"process.executablePath"}
					" -V "
				}
				var_names = "temp_description"
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					exclude_lines_pattern = "sh:"
					selected_positions = 1
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "clean short_description"
			set_attr {
				"short_description"
				eval {"javascript:
var rtrn = \"\";
var array = ${temp_description};
var i;
for (i=0; i<array.size() ; i++)	
	rtrn = rtrn  + \" \\n\" + array.get(i); "}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "reference to enrich library"
			ref {refid = "118e7a04e4d4441ba0e64e4d0e3338d7"}
		}
		step {
			name = "set process_ids"
			set_attr {
				"process_ids"
				get_attr {"process.pid"}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "set type"
			set_attr {
				"type"
				"Apache"
			}
		}
	}
	connection {
		name = "create Proxy Connections"
		step {
			name = "verify Proxy entries"
			parse_text_file_to_var {
				file_path = get_files_by_filter {
					expression = get_attr {"config_file"}
					foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
				}
				var_names = "dummy"
				parsing_strategy = regex_parsing {regex = "^LoadModule (proxy.*)"}
				if_not_found_do = terminate {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "build include tables"
			parse_text_file_to_var {
				file_path = get_files_by_filter {
					expression = get_attr {"config_file"}
					foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
				}
				var_names = table {
					name = "inc_tbl"
					col_names = "files"
				}
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					include_lines_pattern = "Include"
					exclude_lines_pattern = "^#|^$"
					delimiters = " "
					selected_positions = 2
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "filter relative paths"
			filter {
				src_table_name = "inc_tbl"
				target_table_name = "inc_tbl_temp"
				condition = not_starts_with {
					"/"
					get_attr {"inc_tbl[].files"}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "keep fixed entries"
			filter {
				src_table_name = "inc_tbl"
				target_table_name = "inc_tbl"
				condition = starts_with {
					"/"
					get_attr {"inc_tbl[].files"}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "rebuild entries in temp folder"
			transform {
				src_table_name = "inc_tbl_temp"
				target_table_name = "inc_tbl_temp"
				operation {set_field {
						field_name = "files"
						value = concat {
							get_attr {"install_directory"}
							"/"
							get_attr {"inc_tbl_temp[].files"}
						}
					}}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "union tables"
			union {
				table1_name = "inc_tbl"
				table2_name = "inc_tbl_temp"
				result_table_name = "inc_tbl"
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "create conf_file table"
			parse_var_to_var {
				from_var_name = "config_file"
				to_var_names = table {
					name = "inc_tbl_temp"
					col_names = "files"
				}
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					selected_positions = 1
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "union tables"
			union {
				table1_name = "inc_tbl"
				table2_name = "inc_tbl_temp"
				result_table_name = "inc_tbl"
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "get proxy entries"
			parse_text_file_to_var {
				file_path = get_files_by_filter {
					expression = get_attr {"inc_tbl[*].files"}
					foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
				}
				var_names = table {
					name = "proxy_cluster"
					col_names = "str"
				}
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					include_lines_pattern = "<Proxy balancer|BalancerMember|ProxyPass|ProxyPassReverse|RewriteRule|<Virtual|Listen"
					exclude_lines_pattern = "^#|^$|Instance|ProxyPassReverseCookieDomain"
					selected_positions = 1
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "get server name"
			parse_text_file_to_var {
				file_path = get_files_by_filter {
					expression = get_attr {"inc_tbl[*].files"}
					foreach_attribute_name = "forEach"
				}
				var_names = table {
					name = "server_names"
					col_names = "server"
				}
				parsing_strategy = delimited_parsing {
					include_lines_pattern = "ServerName"
					delimiters = " "
					selected_positions = 2
				}
				if_not_found_do = nop {}
				cache_flag = 0
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "filter table server name"
			filter {
				src_table_name = "server_names"
				target_table_name = "server_names"
				condition = any {
					eq {
						get_attr {"server_names[].server"}
						get_attr {"entry_point.host_name"}
					}
					contains {
						get_attr {"server_names[].server"}
						"usdo2.ihsenergy.com"
					}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "filter table server name needed"
			filter {
				src_table_name = "inc_tbl"
				target_table_name = "inc_tbl"
				condition = any {
					ends_with {
						"httpd.conf"
						get_attr {"inc_tbl[].files"}
					}
					contains {
						get_attr {"inc_tbl[].files"}
						get_attr {"server_names[].forEach"}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "create proxy entries"
			filter {
				src_table_name = "proxy_cluster"
				target_table_name = "proxy_entries"
				condition = any {
					starts_with {
						"BalancerMember"
						get_attr {"proxy_cluster[].str"}
					}
					starts_with {
						"Proxy"
						get_attr {"proxy_cluster[].str"}
					}
					starts_with {
						"Listen"
						get_attr {"proxy_cluster[].str"}
					}
					starts_with {
						"<Virtual"
						get_attr {"proxy_cluster[].str"}
					}
				}
			}
		}
		step {
			name = "Filter Proxy Entries"
